&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hearing is a &lt;strong&gt;natural phenomenon&lt;/strong&gt; to normal ears.  &lt;br&gt;
Listening is a &lt;strong&gt;conscious phenomenon&lt;/strong&gt; from a willing mind.  &lt;br&gt;
It is possible that with a normal ear I can hear but not listen.  &lt;br&gt;
And it is also possible that with a deaf ear I may not hear but listen.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
